Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Signal, the\Ngreatest robot I've ever created!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! It's a robot in\Nthe form of a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's built with state\Nof the art technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and also has a fighting\Nprogram for combat tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, his Mira technology body is\Ncovered with a flexible metal I invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's possible to make\Nmore natural, human movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can it move?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.21,0:00:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will program the\Npersonality to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:01:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want someone\Nreliable, like a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that will make\Nhim somewhat like a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes, it's Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my big bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay... yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, I'm tired of the usual praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you angry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cause I can't catch fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, that's boring, fishing is so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It satisfies your hunger! You\Ncan't eat stones, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you satisfy\Nyour hunger by fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can understand a\Nstrong, high-spirited, solitary fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, there is no fighting philosophy, no\Nspirit of victory, no formidable opponents!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it, I hate this\Ncountryside with nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace doesn't work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This trembling fist,\Nburning passion and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wilt without\Nusing my incredible power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal has changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, because you\Nsneezed during the programming...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mira system must have a bug, and\Ninterprets it as a command to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Signal will\Ntransform when I sneeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Nobuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the sea, it's the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the sea, it's a lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lake with lots of sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's getting eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Nobuhiko Otoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents went to study abroad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I came to my grandpa's\Nhouse in the town of Dokari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, copying finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the plum colored one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to leave it as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Nobuhiko,\NSignal, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate, chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Mini!\NChocolate, chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Mini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chris, I'm hungry!\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chris, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got any snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate, chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she in the lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, wait up Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay, she's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's in the study.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alley-oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of that branch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this run-down room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so disgusted\Nwith your way of sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, this doesn't happen\Nno matter how much I toss and turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to come up with some\Npoor excuse, help me clean a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a weak girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Physical labor is not good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one girl who came to\Nme and wanted to be my apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she would\Ndo anything, even cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a beautiful super-smart\Ngirl, a super-smart beautiful girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one and only super\Nsmart beautiful scientist, Chris Sine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, take care of the cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I have such a good apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fine day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can a robot possibly tell the\Ndifference between rainy and fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel all rusty when it is raining out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you spray yourself\Nwith some water-proof coating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I' m going out for patrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't he let a\Ncleaning robot take care of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than Signal, I don't\Nknow of any robots in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if there was a robot\Nin this house, it wouldn't perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The robot would be useless, and\Nwouldn't be able to do complicated tasks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you\Nmake one by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What grandpa was saying reminded\Nme that you' re robot scientist yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see a small\Nproject like a cleaning robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so show me what you\Nmean by making a perfect robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's only if you could, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't claim to be a\Nbeautiful robot scientist for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the right time comes,\Nwhen the right time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the right time comes, I will\Nmake such a perfect super robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...out of jealousy, the\Nprofessor told me not to use his lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just hates my talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just complaining?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying or\Ncomplaining, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even a fool knows Signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Signal to rescue the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my name is Signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... what a messy room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That... useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Chris, good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't use the lab\Non your own, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone got the Mira data.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the album?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you have such\Nan old picture of Signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobuhiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't you remember\Nyour own father's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it looks so much different now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that picture is\Nfrom more than 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A while ago, me and\NMasanobu made a test robot together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We designed its face after Masanobu's\Nto avoid the trouble of making a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Signal's face was\Nmade based on the same model.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I was just made as rehash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your insides are built from\Nthe state of the art Mira model.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, I want to see that robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not here,\NMasanobu took it with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My prototype model...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that makes it like my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.63,0:13:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will see him sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is perhaps... yes, Pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's Pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Elara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Elara, you came to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, she came to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, is the Professor in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my maintenance day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll take you to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not fair, Signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to start all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Ms. Elara, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me with the cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fighting robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not programmed to clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mess is because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what happened to this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this messy room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better start cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bad, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like\Nit, but I really am neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:14:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, despite my looks, I love cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy having an adolescent moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how you handle cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal has a thing for Elara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go use the\Ntoilet, do so during this break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, here in the town of\NDokari its peaceful with no crime at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it stays like this, there'll be no\Nchance for me to show off my true abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hate robots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man down there is bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Otoi Robot Lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Nobuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound well yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, things are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Nobuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, are you well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'm fine, but aren't\Nyou lonely away from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa made me a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I doing this?\NGrandpa made me a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I doing this?\N...just like a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\N...just like a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobuhiko, how about my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the middle of\Ndoing maintenance on Elara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.39,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody who rarely calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masanobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time\Nyou called since you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that no news is good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means there's something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong with you, officer Shinjo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you wearing\Nyour summer clothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal, you're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my precious handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal has been with me all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who\Nattacked me suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a quick glance,\Nbut that figure, that style...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could it have been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was probably not Signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse was stolen from Masanobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that a robot\Nwas stolen from Professor Otoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but why would a stolen\Nrobot from overseas be in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I' m not sure why.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the program had a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the cause, we\Nbetter find the robot and bring it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's really Pulse,\Nonly I will be able to capture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it gives you trouble,\Ndon't treat it too roughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Pulse are\Nboth my precious sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all right, I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Signal, do you really understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do the research at our end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the trouble, but\Nplease take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Otoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dad again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to talk to grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give him my message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, it's big news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A super high-tech blade and\Na mini-laser is attached to Pulse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masanobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you build such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want a strong robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse is really strong now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How well I've learned from my Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Minoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're looking for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we find it, we will call you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse is here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse has already gotten here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a kid with no common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\NThere's a kid with no common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a kid with no common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:20:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I am Signal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not me, that's a white birch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse is so near-sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done\Nbragging about my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he your pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, forgive me, Pulse!\NIsn't he your pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, forgive me, Pulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.06,0:21:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have some old data on Pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this floppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Pulse, the Professor\Nasked me to take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Professor Otoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be Dr.\NUmanokoji Hoshimaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umenokoji Hoshimaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The robot called Pulse\Nwhich you created, is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that you stole Pulse?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I hate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I ordered Pulse to\Ndestroy your precious Signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you fighting with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We' re brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've no reason to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal, The only thing l\Nknow is that I must destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.71,0:23:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.95,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Pulse just a prototype of Signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, isn't Signal technically better?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only if Masanobu\Nhadn't changed anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At present, Pulse is a lethal weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A walking knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal's materials can be torn by his\Nmono-molecular cutter or burnt by his laser!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and look for Signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nobuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The robot you created will be\Ndestroyed by another of your creations!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how that feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This data will...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-destruct?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This data produces a\Ncomputer virus automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.88,0:24:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Look forward to seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.69,0:24:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done, Dr. Umanokoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.29,0:24:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.06,0:24:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.26,0:24:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the Professor to his bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.53,0:24:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.24,0:24:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.00,0:24:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys bring the data and\Nhe brings the actual materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.14,0:24:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.92,0:24:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal, Signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.56,0:25:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.15,0:25:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose the time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.75,0:25:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal, Signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.83,0:25:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The movement of the blade in his arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.65,0:25:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.07,0:27:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.20,0:27:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elara was kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.27,0:28:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right Epsilon, Gatling Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.37,0:28:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the enemy, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.81,0:28:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.71,0:28:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.18,0:28:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elara!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.78,0:28:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Twin Signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.58,0:28:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Family Game Runs Wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.39,0:28:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit sulking and do something, Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.92,0:28:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth?
